com.caverock.androidsvg

Class SVGImageView

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.view.View
      • android.widget.ImageView
        • com.caverock.androidsvg.SVGImageView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drawable.Callback, AccessibilityEventSource, KeyEvent.Callback

    public class SVGImageView
extends ImageView
    SVGImageView is a View widget that allows users to include SVG images in their layouts. It is implemented as a thin layer over android.widget.ImageView.

    XML attributes

    svg
    A resource reference, or a file name, of an SVG in your application
    css
    Optional extra CSS to apply when rendering the SVG
